data.description: Welcome to this impeccably designed single-story home in the gated Weston Reserve Community offers a spacious 4-Bedroom layout and a private enclosed Screened Porch Patio. Enhanced by professional landscaping, it boasts a unique backyard view overlooking the community pool, playground, and volleyball sand court.  Nestled in a secure and well-established neighborhood near The LOOP's shopping and dining, with Publix Supermarket just a stroll away, convenience meets comfort. Strategically located minutes from Disney, International Drive, and Orlando International Airport, this residence features top-of-the-line LG appliances and elegant laminate flooring in the bedrooms and dining room.  To discover the charm and comfort of this home, call now to schedule a private showing! This can be your dream home!
